```plantuml
@startuml victor369basu_Real-time-stock-market-prediction
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor "User"

package "Stock Market Prediction System" {
  rectangle "Kafka" {
    rectangle "Producer" as Producer #orange
    rectangle "Kafka Topic\n (Stock Data)" as StockTopic #lightgrey
    rectangle "Consumer" as Consumer #orange
    rectangle "ML Consumer" as MLConsumer #orange
  }

  rectangle "Data Preprocessing" {
    rectangle "MinMaxScalar" as PreProcess #lightblue
  }

  rectangle "TensorFlow.js" {
    rectangle "LSTM Model" as LSTM #lightyellow
    rectangle "Model Trainer" as ModelTrainer #lightyellow
    rectangle "Model Validator" as ModelValidator #lightyellow
  }

  rectangle "MongoDB" as MongoDB #lightgreen

  rectangle "Node.js Server" {
    rectangle "HTTP Server" as HTTPServer #lightpink
    rectangle "Socket.IO" as SocketIO #lightpink
  }
}

User --> HTTPServer : Request training/validation
HTTPServer --> SocketIO : Communicate with client
Producer --> StockTopic : Publish stock data
StockTopic --> Consumer : Consume stock data
Consumer --> MongoDB : Store data
StockTopic --> MLConsumer : Consume stock data
MLConsumer --> PreProcess : Preprocess data
MLConsumer --> LSTM : Real-time prediction
LSTM --> MongoDB : Log predictions
ModelTrainer --> MongoDB : Retrieve training data
ModelTrainer --> LSTM : Train model
ModelValidator --> MongoDB : Retrieve test data
ModelValidator --> LSTM : Validate model
LSTM --> MongoDB : Store performance metrics
@enduml
```